# Materials and services

1. Plexiglass > Properties: 
	- color (selectbox with following options: "beli", "opal beli", "providni", "crni"); 
	- thickness (selectbox with following options 1mm, 2mm, 3mm, 5mm, 8mm, 10mm, 15mm, 20mm);
	- width (input box with numerical value in millimeters);
	- height (input box with numerical value in millimeters);
	- laser cut line lentgh (input box with numerical value in millimeters)

2. Led Neon > Properties:
	- color (selectbox with following options: "RGB", "toplo beli", "hladno beli", "crveni", "žuti");
	- length (input box with numerical value in millimeters);

3. Printer > Properties:
	- media (selectbox with following options: "bela mat", "bela sjaj", "providna mat", "providna sjaj", "baner folija" );
	- width (input box with numerical value in millimeters);
	- height (input box with numerical value in millimeters);

4. Cutter > Properties:
	- media (selectbox with following options: "obična", "reflektujuća");
	- area (input box with numerical value in square meters);




- `App.js` used for import other scripts and form the template
- `Item.js` used to display one item and its properties.
- `Items.js` used to import components: `ItemList.js` and `ItemCreate.js` and create a items list.
- `ItemList.js` -vue file with `v-for` to create list
- `ItemCreate.js` input box and submit button to create new item

